title: TikToker Josh Woods Performs After Bobby saw him Singing at a Car wash on TikTok + Eddie Risks His Eyebrows for a Chance To Win Money + Amy Embarrassed Herself In Front of A Country Star

description:
We've got TikToker Josh Woods on with us right now after Bobby saw him singing at a car wash on TikTok! He also gets a special surprise. Eddie risks his eyebrows for a chance to win money rolling the 100 sided dice we have in the studio. Amy shares a story about how she embarrassed herself in front of Ashley McBryde and made herself look very unprofessional.
